Package fillrbust

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AIPlayer
    Computer controlled player to make choices based of an assignment of risk
    Cards
    A deck of 54 FillRBust cards shuffled randomly
    Dice
    Set of six standard cubic dice with a number on each side.
    The class maintains a record of which dice are selected,
    the score of the selected dice,
    and which dice are reserved from subsequent rolls.
    Dice.Scoreable
    The set of scoreable dice combinations and their values
    DicePanel  
    DicePanel_V
    DicePanel_V Shows the state of the dice graphically.
    FBConfig
    Defines a configuration for FillRBust
    and provides defaults values and IO methods for storing and retrieving it.
    FillRBustGame
    Play the game FillRBust.
    FillrBustGui
    FillrBustGui shows the state of the game by displaying graphical depictions of the players' scores, the card, the dice, the choices, the instructions to the user The state of the game is maintained by the game itself.
